Class AlbumPhoto

java.lang.Object
com.example.model.AlbumPhoto
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AlbumPhoto extends Object implements Serializable
AlbumPhoto is a class that links a Photo to a specific Album. AlbumPhoto allows photos to be arranged in explicit order within the Album.
